<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>The SRS warning light goes off after the primary check, but then comes on.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle">
<ptxt>SRS Warning Light Remains ON</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000YE200SX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>With the ignition switch on (IG), the SRS warning light sometimes comes on after approximately 6 seconds.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle">
<ptxt>SRS Warning Light Remains ON</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000YE200SX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>The SRS warning light always comes on even when DTC is not output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle">
<ptxt>SRS Warning Light Remains ON</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000YE200SX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>With the ignition switch on (IG), the SRS warning light does not come on.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle">
<ptxt>SRS Warning Light does not Come On</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000YE300SX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>Although an SRS warning light operates normally, DTC or a normal system code is not displayed.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle">
<ptxt>Diagnosis Circuit</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM0000014JK00GX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="0" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>Although terminals TC and CG of DLC3 are not connected, DTC or a normal system code is displayed.</ptxt>
</entry>
